========================================================
========================================================
Cubix is a Tetr!s clone written in Python by Baldur Thor Emilsson and Brynjar Magnusson. 
It was made in Computer Science at the Commercial Collage of Iceland. 
It uses OpenGL for the graphics and is portrayed in 3D.

Required modules:
* PyOpenGL: http://pyopengl.sourceforge.net/
* Python Imaging Library (PIL): http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/
* PySQLite: http://www.initd.org/tracker/pysqlite/

New versions, and homepage at:
http://cubix.tveireinir.com

Brynjar Magnusson  // brynjar()brynjar!is // http://brynjar.is
Baldur Thor Emilsson // baldur()baldur!biz // http://baldur.biz
